snippet.title: Godspeed Gameplay
snippet.description:
Gameplay for the Playdate game, Godspeed. ​

Godspeed is a simple game for Playdate, inspired by the movie Speed​. You play as a bus, speeding down a highway full of obstacles, and if you slow down, or crash too much, the bomb explodes. How far can you go?

Download Godspeed here: https://umutseven92.itch.io/godspeed
